Package edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2013.group14.xtraveler.command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Request
    Request interface, send from Client Side to Serverside
    Response
    Response Interface.Define the actions after getting positive response from Server
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddtoVisitedListRequest
    Request class which is called when user wants to add a place into his visited list.
    AddtoWishListRequest
    Request class which is called when user wants to add a place into his wish list.
    GetAttractionRequest
    Request class which is called before switch to Attraction class
    GetAttractionResponse
    Called when get correct response from Server Ready to switch to next page
    GetCityRequest
    Request class which is called when Menu class need information of a specific City from Server
    GetCityResponse
    Called when ready to switch to city page
    GetPersonalInfoRequest
    Called when Client side needs personal information from Server
    GetPersonalInfoResponse
    Called when ready to switch to Personal Information page
    LoginRequest
    Called when user require to login to the app.
    LoginSucResponse
    Called when ready to switch to main page
    NewTravelPlanRequest
    Called when user asks to create a new travel plan Send from Personal Page to Server when "New Plan" button is clicked
    NewTravelPlanResponse
    Called when ready to switch to TravelPlanView page
    SignUpRequest
    Called when a new user filled the form, ready to sign up in the Serverside
